          Use the CORBA predefined sequence types

Tue Apr 25 12:20:12 UTC 2006  Johnny Willemsen  <jwillemsen@remedy.nl>

        * tests/Sequence_Unit_Tests/Sequence_Unit_Tests.mpc:
